dc_description_s: Alternate title: Stadtplan von Bath mit militaergeographischen Eintragungen. Grossblatt 11, Blattbereich 32. Relief shown by 25 meter contour intervals and spot elevations. Gauss-Krueger grid. Legend is in English and German. With a list of abbreviations. Source: Ordnance Survey 1:10,560; 1932, 1936, 1937. Major city access roads are color codes. Accompanied by 35p. booklet: "Militaergeographsche Einzelangaben ueber England; Objektbilder zu den militaergeographischen Objektkarten 1:250 000 und 1:10 000 der Mappe 11 Sued-England"; of photographs and drawings of important military objectives, bridges, factories, etc. (sites are located on map).
